### Incident Reports API — manual checks (SPEC §4 / §7)
### Use with the VS Code "REST Client" extension, or translate to curl.
### Set @apiKey to a plaintext key issued from /admin (Block 7) or seeded for testing.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5173
@apiKey = irk_REPLACE_ME
@id = REPLACE_WITH_ID_FROM_CREATE

### Create — 201 + full report with server id/created_at
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/incidents
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "timestamp": "2026-06-04T18:30:00Z",
  "location": "Laboratorio Central - Mesa 4",
  "incident_type": "DERRAME",
  "severity_level": "MEDIO",
  "chemicals_involved": [
    { "name": "Ácido Acético Glacial", "hazard_class": "Clase B y Clase E", "estimated_quantity": "250 ml" }
  ],
  "actions_taken": [
    "Se evacuó el área inmediata.",
    "Se utilizó equipo de protección personal."
  ],
  "medical_assistance_required": false,
  "status": "ABIERTO"
}

### Invalid payload — 422 with field-level details (bad enum + empty actions_taken)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/incidents
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "timestamp": "2026-06-04T18:30:00Z",
  "location": "Lab",
  "incident_type": "EXPLOSION",
  "severity_level": "MEDIO",
  "actions_taken": [],
  "medical_assistance_required": false,
  "status": "ABIERTO"
}

### Missing / no key — 401 (still logged to api_usage with null key)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/incidents

### List — filters + pagination, excludes soft-deleted
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/incidents?status=ABIERTO&incident_type=DERRAME&limit=10&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### List by date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/incidents?from=2026-01-01T00:00:00Z&to=2026-12-31T23:59:59Z
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Get by id — 200 (404 if unknown or soft-deleted)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/incidents/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

### Patch — status transition persists, bumps updated_at
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/incidents/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "status": "EN_PROGRESO" }

### Patch invalid — 422 (cannot empty actions_taken)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/incidents/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "actions_taken": [] }

### Delete — 204 soft delete (sets deleted_at); subsequent GET ⇒ 404
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/incidents/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
